joNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=997aaa3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://decocare.com</a> 裝修網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkdecoman.com%2Fjsp%2Fmain.jsp&d=4IF1C649KVaN%2BhE9NTL1iQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ec58fb12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp</a> 裝修佬 <br />\n<br />\n以上並非推薦<br />\n<br />\n按揭保險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkmc.com.hk%2Fchi%2Four_business%2Fmortgage_insurance_programme.html&d=4IF1C649KVaN%2BhE9NTL1iQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=efa6efea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html</a><br />\n<br />\n印花稅計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fstamp%2Fstamp_duty_rates.htm&d=4IF1C649KVaN%2BhE9NTL1iQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=808c7100\" target=\"_blank\">http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n男女朋友 可以未婚夫妻名義做按揭<br />\n<br />\n放租要5成按揭<br />\n<br />\ncash rebate 1% vs 1.x% <br />\n<br />\n簡單而言：例子買4m樓，借3.6m<br />\n<br />\n1. 手頭緊： 揀1%cash, loan size 借足 再extra 比1%cash （即 4mx0.6x1% = 24,000)<br />\n<br />\n2. 手頭唔緊： 揀回1.6%， 扣Loan size , 自己成交要比多1.6% 既錢 佢1個月內回返比你 變相同eg1 既loan size 少左 1.6%， 利息少D <br />\n（即 4m x 0.6x 1.6% = 38,400，比起例子1，你成交果陣暫時要比多38,400， 銀行一個月內退返比你）<br />\n<br />\nP.s : 每間銀行計法大致一樣，但都有唔同，例如IXBX, 佢既1.6係多過其他行，詳情問banker<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/163437_9308bb30f865d54df85bcdca3c03f11f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F163437_9308bb30f865d54df85bcdca3c03f11f.jpg&h=b24a7032&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"545368dee1925f781b4339fded3d270d3936a43c","tid":448333,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"【買定唔買？供得起先好買！】低調置業討論區(76)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/446004/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/446004/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nLAST POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15471e5ba079a32d598f824db39640ac7b76cb3","tid":448333,"uid":142966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595b9a88a6cd0e5568b572f8cf533471b7667b76","tid":448333,"uid":154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新地佇立於北角的臨海地標項目前身為前北角邨，現將分兩期發展，第一期住宅項目「海璇」（Victoria Harbour） ，前迎維多利亞港壯麗景色，置身其中令人顧盼自豪。今日新地副董事總經理雷霆及新地代理總經理陳漢麟再次就海璇舉行軟銷記者會，宣布項目銷售部署已進入直路，短期內將亮麗登場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是次假座中環四季酒店舉行記者會，會上雷霆指海璇與系內IFC、 ICC均屬地標。1期分1、2、3、5、5A及6座共355伙，面積約由近300呎起開放式至約2400呎4房雙套房間隔，包括少量花園戶，平台戶等特色單位。<br />\n<br />\n陳漢麟指1、2、3及5座大單位享海景,主打3、4房大戶，面積1200-1600呎，5A及6座提供開放式至3房，景觀以郵輪碼頭及園景為主。晚上大厦外牆有特色燈光裝飾照明。<br />\n<br />\n3及5座對出位置為會所，室內面積約2.8萬呎，提供室內外相連泳池，長約60米外，另有董事屋及多項特色設施。<br />\n<br />\n陳氏指，海璇1200-1600呎大單位約佔百伙，特色戶約佔廿餘伙，彌足珍貴。1期車位達128個。</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d871c9438dddb9d7274bfbc49efd008bbf2e72c2","tid":448333,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aef4c3b8333bb8163bd05ebde8284f918b20416","tid":448333,"uid":142966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64deaddb04b56cc4a43b689da2b6992478071fe4","tid":448333,"uid":48322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新地佇立於北角的臨海地標項目前身為前北角邨，現將分兩期發展，第一期住宅項目「海璇」（Victoria Harbour） ，前迎維多利亞港壯麗景色，置身其中令人顧盼自豪。今日新地副董事總經理雷霆及新地代理總經理陳漢麟再次就海璇舉行軟銷記者會，宣布項目銷售部署已進入直路，短期內將亮麗登場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是次假座中環四季酒店舉行記者會，會上雷霆指海璇與系內IFC、 ICC均屬地標。1期分1、2、3、5、5A及6座共355伙，面積約由近300呎起開放式至約2400呎4房雙套房間隔，包括少量花園戶，平台戶等特色單位。<br />\n<br />\n陳漢麟指1、2、3及5座大單位享海景,主打3、4房大戶，面積1200-1600呎，5A及6座提供開放式至3房，景觀以郵輪碼頭及園景為主。晚上大厦外牆有特色燈光裝飾照明。<br />\n<br />\n3及5座對出位置為會所，室內面積約2.8萬呎，提供室內外相連泳池，長約60米外，另有董事屋及多項特色設施。<br />\n<br />\n陳氏指，海璇1200-1600呎大單位約佔百伙，特色戶約佔廿餘伙，彌足珍貴。1期車位達128個。</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c6f67f409660b6550daa80ab0ca4aaa4e66bb5","tid":448333,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcd89f4e091099c2825eed2c03d6c0ee41c35dd","tid":448333,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocki